      <h1 class="hero-name">L. June Bloch</h1>
      <p class="hero-identity">Anthropologist · Applied AI Builder · World Builder</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">
        <!-- Phase 2: Replace with content from agent briefing + voice document -->
        A humanist who builds — redesigning systems by interrogating constitutive power relations
        and structural violence. Five active research programs spanning Indigenous mound landscapes,
        movement ethnography, anti-trans legislation, recognition and sentience, and AI as a site
        of anthropological inquiry.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-socials">
        <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=9bQ8kjIAAAAJ&hl=en&oi=ao" aria-label="Google Scholar">Scholar</a>
        <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/disabledbydesign.bsky.social" aria-label="Bluesky">Bluesky</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/grouchyseafowl" aria-label="GitHub">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/l-june-bloch-1897a329/" aria-label="LinkedIn">LinkedIn</a>
